      "writtenOn": "2019-02-13T18:34:36Z",
      "side": 0,
      "message": "What do we do if an existing task/job fails one of these sanity checks during the migration?  Presumably we still want it in the new DB, right?  If by some weird chance we do hit one of these cases, I think I\u0027d rather just insert the bad job and not have the migration get interrupted.",
      "parentUuid": "282db4f1_e29c4a97",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 157,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 162,
        "endChar": 3
      },
      "revId": "9d2f2307cb32e355716149661a74c4ad9c52941c",
