      "writtenOn": "2019-02-13T20:34:35Z",
      "side": 0,
      "message": "Ok, that all makes sense to me. My biggest concern is that there\u0027s a bug or an edge case we\u0027re not thinking about, and I would like to know sooner rather than later. If it\u0027s just one random task that\u0027s invalid, I probably wouldn\u0027t worry about it, but if it\u0027s a significant number, there\u0027s probably something wrong.",
